---
title: Spiced Beef & Creamy Pesto Slaw Burger with Kumara Fries
description: It doesn’t get more classic than a beef burger and fries - why don’t we add a twist! A lightly spiced beef mince pattie sits atop a perfectly toasted bun with a a flavourful pesto slaw. Let’s swap out potato for kumara fries and use everyone’s favourite cooking tool to get them extra crisp - the air fryer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6620bdbdd7d86b487f183fd4-dcb6aa04.jpeg
